title: Former MLB player Charles Haeger found dead after police sought him as a suspect in killing of his ex-girlfriend
description: Former MLB player Charles Haeger was found dead in Northern Arizona from a self-inflicted gunshot wound on Saturday after police announced they were searching for him as a suspect in the death of his ex-girlfriend in Scottsdale the previous day, police said.
